    <item>
      <title>持有对冲头寸的华尔街交易员仍受八月危机困扰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/hedged-up-wall-street-traders-still-haunted-by-august-meltdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[看看现在的市场情况，你会发现市场状况良好。股票价格创下历史新高，公司债券没有出现令人担忧的迹象，大宗商品在全球经济乐观情绪的推动下依然保持强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/hedged-up-wall-street-traders-still-haunted-by-august-meltdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 20:25:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
