      <title>菲律宾国家石油公司推迟债券发行，寻求住友贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-11/ecopetrol-taps-sumitomo-loan-after-postponing-dollar-bond-deal</link>
